I"5<p><a href="https://kb.vmware.com/s/article/1022525">Installing VMware Tools in an Ubuntu Virtual Machine (1022525)</a></p>

<ol>
  <li>选择安装Vmware Tools后</li>
  <li>打开VMware Tools CD</li>
  <li>将<code class="highlighter-rouge">VmwareTools.x.x.x-xxxx.tar.gz</code>拷贝到桌面(随便哪里都行，执行时候进入对应路径就行)，解压，得到<code class="highlighter-rouge">vmware-tools-distrib</code>文件夹</li>
  <li>shell执行<code class="highlighter-rouge">sudo Desktop/vmware-tools-distrib/vmware-install.pl -d</code>。重启虚拟机，安装完成。</li>
</ol>

